Tornado[^1]-based, nginx[^2]-friendly proxy server designed to aid and
abet the world-domination pretensions of the wry[^3] project.

Tornado is an asynchronous webserver based on epoll, so epoll is
required for this code to run. I have been using a 256MB rackspace[^4]
cloud server.

[1]: http://github.com/facebook/tornado
[2]: http://nginx.org/en/download.html
[3]: http://github.com/benjamn/wry
[4]: http://www.rackspacecloud.com
